{% comment %}
Snippet for MailChimp subscribe form
For setting go to Admin -> Theme -> Customize Theme -> Product page
- https://docs.shopify.com/manual/configuration/store-customization/communicating-with-customers/accounts-and-newsletters/add-newsletter
